Chat
----

Author:
	Denis Meyer, CallToPower Software

Website:
	https://sites.google.com/site/calltopowersoftware/

Description:
	A chat (server + client) written in JavaScript using node.js, socket.io, jQuery and jQuery mobile.

Version:
	- 1.0.0

Libraries:
	- not included:
	      - node.js
	      - socket.io
	- included:
	      - jQuery v1.9.1
	      - jQuery mobile 1.3.1
	      	- jQuery mobile iOS Theme (https://github.com/taitems/iOS-Inspired-jQuery-Mobile-Theme)

License:
	The MIT License (MIT), see file "LICENSE"

Debug Start:
	- go to src/
	- edit variables in files "server/variables.js" and "client/js/variables.js"
	- start server via
	  	node server/server.js

Release:
	- go to src-release/
	- edit variables in files "server/variables.js" and "client/js/variables.js"
	- obfuscate "client/js/*.js", e.g. via http://javascriptobfuscator.com/
	- start server via
	  	node server/server.js > log.txt &
